Reasoning: The paper discusses the negative impact of social media on society and the need for proactive measures to promote prosocial behavior. This aligns with the themes of social computing (cs.SI) and cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also touches upon issues of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and system design (cs.SD) in the context of regulating social media platforms. Finally, the paper discusses the limitations of regulatory measures, which could fall under the category of computational complexity (cs.CC).
